PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works, of Jerry L. Lampert, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during plesure for a term of three years, effective March 21, 1992, in the place of Dorothy Eleanor Drysdale, whose term will expire.
